<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Seller Account Approved</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #333;">Congratulations, {{name}}!</h1>
  <p>Your seller account has been approved. You can now start listing products on our marketplace.</p>
  <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #ee4d2d; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
    Go to Seller Dashboard
  </a>
  <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Complete your shop profile</li>
    <li>Add your first products</li>
    <li>Set up shipping options</li>
  </ul>
  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;">Welcome to the marketplace! If you have questions, contact our seller support team.</p>
</body>
</html>
